{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Please place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->
{{See|MOS:BADEMPHASIS|MOS:QUOTE}}
{{Template shortcut|Under|Unline|Undline}}
{{high use}}
This template formats a span of text using {{tag|span|params=style="text-decoration: underline;"}}. This adds underlining without the semantics of {{tag|u|link=yes}}.

{{markup
|<nowiki>{{underline|Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur}}</nowiki>
|{{underline|Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur}}
}}

== See also ==

* {{tl|uline}} – wide underline in blue (or specified colour)
* {{tl|uuline}} – double underline
* {{tl|emu}} – for underline {{emu|with}} semantic emphasis
* [[MOS:BADEMPHASIS]]

{{math templates|notation}}

